data.description: Elegantly designed custom Brick home with updated modern interior & amazing views/frontage on #6 FAIRWAY & GREEN of the PIANKATANK RIVER GOLF COURSE. Inviting entry from the covered front porch to great rm w/soaring ceilings, stone fireplc, & gorgeous hardwd floors open to stunning new kitchen w/sleek shaker cabinets, subway tile, granite countertops & Island. Formal & casual dining, Powder rm & fabulous 4 season sunrm leads to expansive patio. Primary BR Ste w/sweeping vaulted ceiling, tiled shower, whirlpool tub & walk-in closet. Gunite pool & meticulously landscaped back yard expanded by the beautiful fairway. Elegant brick 1/2 wall separating pool & golf course all nestled on 1.18ac. Oversized 2 bay, 2 story det'd gar/workshop w/1/2 bath & 14'x 26' 2nd floor for expansion or storage. Aggregate patio, circle driveway & walkways. Gorgeous curb appeal on a quiet cul-de-sac street. Convenient to the golf course's Steamboat Restaurant, YMCA & under 1 hour to Richmond Int'l Airport.
